        "description": "Complete API collection for the grapeminds Public API. Includes all endpoints for wines, producers, regions, region insights, and drinking periods.\n\n**Setup Instructions:**\n1. Set your API key in the collection variables (API_KEY)\n2. Optionally set your preferred language (LANGUAGE: de, en, fr, it)\n3. All requests will automatically use these variables\n\n**Base URL:** https://grapeminds.eu/api/public/v1",
